  "what_to_avoid": "Sets marked 18 months+ as the only option when younger siblings share; tiny construction kits; under-3 choking exclusions; five lookalike wooden cube sets.",
  "methodology": "Benchmarked UK stack-and-crash sets across Lovevery, IKEA UPPSTÅ, Boots Lamaze/Nuby. Captured listing age marks into age_signals. Ranked with buying_factor_memo for two block tower fit, crash joy, brand concentration (max two), and UK buyability. Dual-pass URL smoke + availability on every Top 5 primary on 2026-07-24.",
